eta name=\"robots\" content=\"index, follow\"/><link rel=\"canonical\" href=\"https://a2zconvertor.co.uk/terms\"/><meta property=\"og:title\" content=\"Terms of Service | A2ZConvertor\"/><meta property=\"og:description\" content=\"Terms for using A2ZConvertor&#x27;s browser-based file conversion and editing tools.\"/><meta property=\"og:url\" content=\"https://a2zconvertor.co.uk/terms\"/><meta name=\"twitter:card\" content=\"summary_large_image\"/><meta name=\"twitter:title\" content=\"A2ZConvertor - Free Online Image and PDF Tools\"/><meta name=\"twitter:description\" content=\"Convert, compress and edit images and PDFs online for free.\"/><link rel=\"icon\" href=\"/favicon.ico?favicon.2vob68tjqpejf.ico\" sizes=\"256x256\" type=\"image/x-icon\"/><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/0cz1d0mv5g_q7.js\" noModule=\"\"></script></head><body class=\"min-h-full flex flex-col\"><div hidden=\"\"><!--$--><!--/$--></div><script>try{document.documentElement.dataset.theme=localStorage.getItem(\"a2z-theme\")||\"dark\"}catch{}</script><main class=\"min-h-screen bg-slate-950 text-white\"><nav class=\"sticky top-0 z-50 border-b border-white/10 bg-slate-950/85 backdrop-blur-xl\"><div class=\"mx-auto flex h-20 max-w-7xl items-center justify-between px-6\"><a class=\"text-2xl font-black tracking-tight\" href=\"/\">A2Z<span class=\"text-blue-500\">Convertor</span></a><div class=\"hidden items-center gap-5 text-sm text-slate-300 lg:flex\"><a class=\"transition hover:text-white\" href=\"/tools\">All Tools</a><a class=\"transition hover:text-white\" href=\"/ai-tools\">AI Tools</a><a class=\"transition hover:text-white\" href=\"/image-tools\">Image Tools</a><a class=\"transition hover:text-white\" href=\"/pdf-tools\">PDF Tools</a><a class=\"transition hover:text-white\" href=\"/video-tools\">Video Tools</a><a class=\"transition hover:text-white\" href=\"/audio-tools\">Audio Tools</a><a class=\"transition hover:text-white\" href=\"/text-tools\">Text Tools</a><a class=\"transition hover:text-white\" href=\"/social-media-tools\">Social Tools</a></div><div class=\"hidden items-center gap-3 lg:flex\"><button type=\"button\" aria-label=\"Switch to light theme\" title=\"Switch to light theme\" class=\"inline-flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-full border border-white/15 bg-slate-900 text-xs font-bold\">SUN</button><a class=\"rounded-full bg-blue-600 px-5 py-2.5 text-sm font-semibold text-white shadow-lg shadow-blue-950/30 transition hover:bg-blue-500\" href=\"/request-tool\">Request New Tool</a></div><button type=\"button\" aria-label=\"Toggle navigation menu\" aria-expanded=\"false\" class=\"inline-flex h-11 w-11 items-center justify-center rounded-full border border-white/10 bg-slate-900 text-white lg:hidden\"><span class=\"flex w-5 flex-col gap-1.5\"><span class=\"h-0.5 rounded-full bg-current\"></span><span class=\"h-0.5 rounded-full bg-current\"></span><span class=\"h-0.5 rounded-full bg-current\"></span></span></button></div></nav><section class=\"px-6 py-20\"><div class=\"mx-auto max-w-4xl\"><div class=\"mb-10 rounded-3xl border border-white/10 bg-slate-900/70 p-8\"><p class=\"mb-3 text-sm font-semibold uppercase text-blue-300\">Last updated: June 17, 2026</p><h1 class=\"mb-4 text-5xl font-black tracking-tight\">Terms of Service</h1><p class=\"max-w-3xl text-lg leading-8 text-slate-300\">These terms explain responsible use of A2ZConvertor, including browser-based processing, file responsibility and service availability.</p></div><div class=\"grid gap-5 text-slate-300\"><section class=\"rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-slate-900/60 p-6\"><h2 class=\"mb-3 text-2xl font-bold text-white\">Using A2ZConvertor</h2><div class=\"space-y-4 leading-7 text-slate-300\"><p>A2ZConvertor provides free online tools for file conversion, compression, editing and inspection. No account is required. Many tools run directly in your browser where possible.</p></div></section><section class=\"rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-slate-900/60 p-6\"><h2 class=\"mb-3 text-2xl font-bold text-white\">Acceptable use</h2><div class=\"space-y-4 leading-7 text-slate-300\"><p>You agree to use A2ZConvertor lawfully and responsibly. You may not use the site to upload, process, create or distribute illegal, harmful, abusive, infringing or unauthorized content, or to interfere with the site, its security or other users.</p></div></section><section class=\"rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-slate-900/60 p-6\"><h2 class=\"mb-3 text-2xl font-bold text-white\">Your responsibility for files</h2><div class=\"space-y-4 leading-7 text-slate-300\"><p>You are responsible for the files you choose, the rights you have to use them and the results you download. Do not process files that you are not allowed to use or that contain sensitive information you are not comfortable handling in a browser tool.</p></div></section><section class=\"rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-slate-900/60 p-6\"><h2 class=\"mb-3 text-2xl font-bold text-white\">No illegal content</h2><div class=\"space-y-4 leading-7 text-slate-300\"><p>A2ZConvertor must not be used for unlawful purposes, including copyright infringement, privacy violations, malware, harassment or processing content that violates applicable laws.</p></div></section><section class=\"rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-slate-900/60 p-6\"><h2 class=\"mb-3 text-2xl font-bold text-white\">No warranty</h2><div class=\"space-y-4 leading-7 text-slate-300\"><p>A2ZConvertor is provided as-is and as available. We aim to keep tools useful and accurate, but we do not guarantee that any tool will be error-free, uninterrupted, secure or suitable for a particular purpose. Always review output files before relying on them.</p></div></section><section class=\"rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-slate-900/60 p-6\"><h2 class=\"mb-3 text-2xl font-bold text-white\">Limitation of liability</h2><div class=\"space-y-4 leading-7 text-slate-300\"><p>To the fullest extent permitted by law, A2ZConvertor will not be liable for indirect, incidental, consequential or special damages, loss of data, loss of profits or issues caused by your use of downloaded files or third-party services.</p></div></section><section class=\"rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-slate-900/60 p-6\"><h2 class=\"mb-3 text-2xl font-bold text-white\">Service availability</h2><div class=\"space-y-4 leading-7 text-slate-300\"><p>We may change, suspend or discontinue parts of the site at any time. Some tools depend on browser support and may not work with every file, codec or device.</p></div></section><section class=\"rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-slate-900/60 p-6\"><h2 class=\"mb-3 text-2xl font-bold text-white\">Intellectual property</h2><div class=\"space-y-4 leading-7 text-slate-300\"><p>The A2ZConvertor site design, branding and original content belong to A2ZConvertor or its licensors. You keep whatever rights you already have in the files you process with the tools.</p></div></section><section class=\"rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-slate-900/60 p-6\"><h2 class=\"mb-3 text-2xl font-bold text-white\">Changes to the service or terms</h2><div class=\"space-y-4 leading-7 text-slate-300\"><p>We may update tools, pages and these terms as the service evolves. Continued use of the site after changes means you accept the updated terms.</p></div></section><section class=\"rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-slate-900/60 p-6\"><h2 class=\"mb-3 text-2xl font-bold text-white\">Contact</h2><div class=\"space-y-4 leading-7 text-slate-300\"><p>General questions: <a href=\"mailto:info@a2zconvertor.co.uk\" class=\"font-semibold text-blue-300 hover:text-blue-200\">info@a2zconvertor.co.uk</a><br/>Support: <a href=\"mailto:support@a2zconvertor.co.uk\" class=\"font-semibold text-blue-300 hover:text-blue-200\">support@a2zconvertor.co.uk</a><br/>Contact: <a href=\"mailto:contact@a2zconvertor.co.uk\" class=\"font-semibold text-blue-300 hover:text-blue-200\">contact@a2zconvertor.co.uk</a></p></div></section></div></div></section><footer class=\"border-t border-white/10 px-6 py-16\"><div class=\"mx-auto mb-12 max-w-7xl\"><section class=\"rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-slate-900/70 p-5\"><div class=\"\"><h2 class=\"text-xl font-black\">Get new free tools and productivity tips.</h2><p class=\"mt-3 max-w-2xl leading-7 text-slate-400\">Be first to know when we launch new converters, PDF tools and browser-based productivity tools.</p><form class=\"mt-5 flex gap-3 flex-col\"><label class=\"sr-only\" for=\"_R_tbsnlb_\">Email address</label><input id=\"_R_tbsnlb_\" type=\"email\" required=\"\" autoComplete=\"email\" placeholder=\"you@example.com\" class=\"min-w-0 flex-1 rounded-xl border border-white/10 bg-slate-950 px-4 py-3 text-white outline-none focus:border-blue-500\" name=\"email\" value=\"\"/><input type=\"hidden\" name=\"source\" value=\"a2zconvertor\"/><button type=\"submit\" class=\"rounded-xl bg-blue-600 px-5 py-3 font-semibold text-white hover:bg-blue-500\">Join by email</button></form><p class=\"mt-3 text-xs leading-5 text-slate-500\">No newsletter provider is connected yet. This opens your email app; we do not fake a stored subscription.</p></div></section></div><div class=\"mx-auto grid max-w-7xl gap-10 md:grid-cols-4\"><div><h3 class=\"mb-4 text-2xl font-black\">A2Z<span class=\"text-blue-500\">Convertor</span></h3><p class=\"text-slate-400\">Free online tools to convert, compress and edit files quickly.</p></div><div><h4 class=\"mb-4 font-bold\">Categories</h4><ul class=\"space-y-2 text-slate-400\"><li><a class=\"transition hover:text-white\" href=\"/tools\">All Tools</a></li><li><a class=\"transition hover:text-white\" href=\"/image-tools\">Image Tools</a></li><li><a class=\"transition hover:text-white\" href=\"/pdf-tools\">PDF Tools</a></li><li><a class=\"transition hover:text-white\" href=\"/video-tools\">Video Tools</a></li><li><a class=\"transition hover:text-white\" href=\"/audio-tools\">Audio Tools</a></li><li><a class=\"transition hover:text-white\" hr